{
  "stem": "19352.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I came to Prague.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In Prague we had Russians going around.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were guards, just Czech guards.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I asked him to take care of me because the Russians are too close.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They're coming too close to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't want them to came close.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And one has even money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He-- he said, see, I have money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I said, good for you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You're rich.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You're not supposed to be rich.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "A Russian not supposed to be rich-- [INAUDIBLE] money.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "This man, when I went to the information desk, they served you also bread and some kind of a marmalade.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I didn't want marmalade.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I want coffee.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I want a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He saw that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he said, come, I will to show you where the uprising in Prague was.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So he show me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then, later on, he said, I go home, and I will come back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You go and stay close to this lady from this-- I told her that you are afraid of the Russians.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Thank God.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I-- he went home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He brought a sandwich, you know, for me to have a sandwich.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he waited until 6 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he put me in a train who goes to [?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Terezina. ?] When you found your brother there, what did you and your brother-- where did-- what did you do then?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Where did you go?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I came to this village.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is a village.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this is what-- a [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and it was very hard to go in because this was a quarantine that time-- typhus and-- and dysentery.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I have the cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I said to this Czech-- the first was Czech.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
